3.3 Get product detail

GET /api/public/v1/catalog/products/{slug}

Response includes:
	•	Product core fields
	•	Full image gallery
	•	Primary + additional categories
	•	Linked products (pseudo-variants) if present

Response (example):

{
  "id": "uuid",
  "name": "Lipstick – Red",
  "slug": "lipstick-red",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "shortDescription": "...",
  "priceCents": 45000,
  "currency": "COP",
  "sku": "COCO-000123",
  "attributes": { "shade": "Red", "finish": "Matte" },
  "primaryCategory": { "id": "uuid", "slug": "makeup", "name": "Makeup" },
  "categories": [
    { "id": "uuid", "slug": "sale", "name": "Sale" }
  ],
  "images": [
    { "url": "https://...", "altText": "...", "sortOrder": 0, "isPrimary": true },
    { "url": "https://...", "altText": "...", "sortOrder": 1, "isPrimary": false }
  ],
  "linkedProducts": {
    "groupId": "uuid",
    "optionName": "Color",
